   [$ (^Jacin.^) $] I will, I will, and am heartily glad of it.
[$ (^Exit^) Jacintha.$]
   [$ (^Frank.^) $] [$ (^Advancing^) $] May be so -- But you and I   #
shall
have a few Words before you get off so cleanly.
   [$ (^Clar.^) $] [$ (^Advancing.^) $] How lucky it was I came home
<P 33>
at this Instant. I shall spoil his Sport, I believe. Do
