   [$ (^Frank.^) $] I am amaz'd! You here! This was 
unexpected indeed!
   [$ (^Clar.^) $] Why, I believe I do come a little unexpectedly;
 but I shall amaze you more -- I know the whole Course
of your Amour; all the Process of your mighty Passion
